com.github.jmkgreen.morphia.mapping
Interface Mapper

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultMapper
public interface Mapper

Maps POJOs and MongoDB DBObjects. Holds a list of EntityInterceptors that are invoked during lifecycle phases across all mapped entity classes.

Implementations should be thread-safe.
